data.description: Charming Craftsman Home in Ideal Klamath Falls Location! Discover timeless elegance in this classic Craftsman-style gem, perfectly situated in the heart of Klamath Falls, Oregon. With 1606 sq. ft. of living space, this home offers the ideal blend of vintage character and modern comfort. Step inside to find craftsmanship at every turn, from the original hardwood floors to the detailed trim. The cozy living room boasts a beautiful fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for gatherings. Enjoy the Oregon outdoors in the backyard, a peaceful oasis, perfect for summer BBQs and relaxation. What truly sets this home apart is its location. Close to everything Klamath Falls has to offer, you'll have easy access to shops, restaurants, parks, and more. Plus, the picturesque views of the surrounding landscape. Don't miss this opportunity to own a piece of Klamath Falls history with all the modern amenities you desire. Schedule you're viewing today and experience the magic of Craftsman
